  {
    "text": "Why Bittensor Goes Nuclear in 2026 \n\nImagine one giant marketplace where thousands of AI teams compete to be the best at ONE specific job.\n\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 One subnet does super-long memory (Quasar SN24 \u00e2\u0080\u0094 just signed its first enterprise client)  \n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 One subnet rents cheap GPUs on demand",
