    "text": "The $TAO Bittensor ecosystem is as fascinating as it is complex. A lot of people want exposure to $dTAO to explore the subnets environment, but they don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t even know where to begin.\n\nIs that you? Start with the Top 8. Investing? No, genius. Studying, at first. Understand what each",
